snippet.title: SpinSling Launch Trailer!
snippet.description:
oar through the magical world of SpinSling as you escape the clutches of evil! With the powerful magic that binds them together, the little critters must spin and sling their way past bombs, spikes, misplaced explosive sheep and more!

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Retrogene.SpinSling&hl=en
